			At Expletive Studios, we're a little <b>!%£@?&amp;#</b> indie with big <b>!%£@?&amp;#</b> dreams. Founded around a kitchen table with a lot of coffee; we started out as a bunch of friends with an idea to make a game. A game that would be the spiritual successor of sorts to some of our favorites with tastely unique and memorable additions. Fast-forward six years of concepting and garnering experience, college and multiple jobs, all the while making consistent progress.
		</p>

	</div>
</div>

<div class="banner__full-width">
